items.name: static let hostKey: StreamSOCKSProxyConfiguration
items.desc: Value is an NSString object that represents the SOCKS proxy host.

items.name: static let passwordKey: StreamSOCKSProxyConfiguration
items.desc: Value is an NSString object containing the user’s password.

items.name: static let portKey: StreamSOCKSProxyConfiguration
items.desc: Value is an NSNumber object containing an integer that represents the port on which the proxy listens.

items.name: static let userKey: StreamSOCKSProxyConfiguration
items.desc: Value is an NSString object containing the user’s name.

items.name: static let versionKey: StreamSOCKSProxyConfiguration
items.desc: Value is either NSStreamSOCKSProxyVersion4 or NSStreamSOCKSProxyVersion5.
